com.facebook.proguard.annotations

注释类型 DoNotStrip


  • @Target(value={TYPE,FIELD,METHOD,CONSTRUCTOR})
 @Retention(value=CLASS)
public @interface DoNotStrip
    Add this annotation to a class, method, or field to instruct Proguard to not strip it out. This is useful for methods called via reflection that could appear as unused to Proguard.
